    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## GUÍA RÁPIDA DE USO\n",
    "\n",
    "### Para Ejecutar la Demostración:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "# 1. Navegar a la carpeta del proyecto\n",
    "cd \"Proyecto Vision Celulas\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. Instalar dependencias\n",
    "pip install -r requirements.txt\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. Ejecutar el script unificado\n",
    "python prueba_unificada.py\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Para Instalar como Paquete:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "# Desde la carpeta del proyecto\n",
    "pip install .\n",
    "\n",
    "# Luego en cualquier script Python:\n",
    "import cell_segmentation_lib as lib\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Para Clonar desde GitHub:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "git clone https://github.com/hssacrament-ui/Proyecto-Analisis-de-Celulas-desde-Imagenes-Microscopio-.git\n",
    "cd Proyecto-Analisis-de-Celulas-desde-Imagenes-Microscopio-\n",
    "pip install -r requirements.txt\n",
    "python prueba_unificada.py\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## FUNCIONES PRINCIPALES DISPONIBLES\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# Preprocesamiento\n",
    "rgb_to_gray(img_rgb)                    # Conversión RGB → Gris\n",
    "intensity_transform(image, gamma)       # Corrección Gamma\n",
    "spatial_filter_gaussian(image, size, sigma)  # Filtro Gaussiano\n",
    "frequency_filter_lowpass(image, cutoff)     # Filtro Pasa-Bajos FFT\n",
    "\n",
    "# Detección\n",
    "edge_detection_sobel(image)             # Bordes con Sobel\n",
    "point_detection(image, threshold)       # Detección de puntos\n",
    "hough_lines_manual(edge_image)          # Hough para líneas\n",
    "hough_circles_manual(edge_image, r_min, r_max)  # Hough para círculos\n",
    "\n",
    "# Segmentación\n",
    "otsu_threshold(image)                   # Umbralización Otsu\n",
    "label_components(binary_image)          # Etiquetado de componentes\n",
    "\n",
    "# Conteo\n",
    "count_cells(labels, min_area)           # Conteo de células\n",
    "```"
